com.blukii.sdk.config

Enum BlukiiAction

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<BlukiiAction>
      • com.blukii.sdk.config.BlukiiAction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<BlukiiAction>

    public enum BlukiiAction
extends java.lang.Enum<BlukiiAction>
    Enum BlukiiAction represents the family of actions which can be done on blukiis.

    Note: Whether the action is possible depends on the blukii module and firmware version.

    See Also:
    Blukii.check(BlukiiAction)
